<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Smart Stock Predictor</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <style>
    body {
      background-image: url('https://img.freepik.com/premium-vector/business-candle-stick-graph-chart-stock-market-investment_41981-866.jpg?semt=ais_items_boosted&w=740');
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      background-attachment: fixed;
    }

    .glass {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
      backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
      border-radius: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    }

    .glow-button {
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #3b82f6, #6366f1);
      box-shadow: 0 0 12px #3b82f6;
    }

    .glow-button:hover {
      box-shadow: 0 0 18px #6366f1;
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    .animated-gradient {
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #3b82f6, #6366f1);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      animation: slide 4s infinite alternate;
    }

    @keyframes slide {
      from {
        background-position: 0%;
      }
      to {
        background-position: 100%;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="text-gray-800">
  <div class="flex items-center justify-center min-h-screen px-6">
    <div class="glass max-w-3xl w-full p-10 text-center">
      
      <!-- Title -->
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-extrabold animated-gradient mb-4">Smart Stock Predictor</h1>
      
      <!-- Tagline -->
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 font-medium mb-6">An intelligent, AI-powered solution for forecasting market trends.</p>

      <!-- Description -->
      <p class="text-base text-gray-800 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        Smart Stock Predictor is an AI-driven platform designed to forecast stock market prices using historical trends,
        real-time data, and financial sentiment. Built for both novice and expert investors, the system offers stock price prediction,
        explainability, risk scoring, and future integration with crypto and commodity markets. 
        It's accurate, scalable, and tailored for decision-making in dynamic financial environments.
      </p>

      <!-- Login Button -->
      <a href="/authentication" class="inline-block glow-button text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-xl transition transform duration-300">
        üîê Login to Continue
      </a>

      <!-- Footer -->
      <p class="mt-10 text-sm text-gray-600">&copy; 2025 Smart Stock Predictor | Built for IIITM Gwalior Hackathon</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>